sourcesContent: import { Component, Input, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { JwtClientService } from '../jwt-client.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-edit-task', templateUrl: './edit-task.component.html', styleUrls: ['./edit-task.component.css'] }) export class EditTaskComponent implements OnInit{ public task:any; constructor(private service:JwtClientService){ this.task=service.getTask(); } ngOnInit(): void { console.log("this",this.task) } }
